•	Provides a Sales Performance Dashboard to analyze overall business sales and profitability.
•	Displays key KPIs including Revenue, Profit, Orders Count, and Units Sold.
•	Shows monthly revenue trends to track sales growth over time.
•	Highlights regional sales performance across East, North, West, and South regions.
•	Identifies top customers based on net sales and purchase volume.
•	Analyzes revenue contribution by product categories.
•	Compares sales performance across different sales channels (Online, Retail Store, Corporate Sales, Marketplace).
•	Includes interactive filters to explore data by region.
•	Helps identify high-performing products, customers, and regions.
•	Enables quick data-driven insights for business decision-making.
